"{\"uid\": \"vision.org.au-read-news-french-police-arrest-christians-over-olympics-opening-ceremony-protest\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Listen  Read  Watch  Interact  About  Christian News  byTony Davenport|Aug 8, 2024  French police have arrested seven Spanish Christians for a peaceful protest over the Olympic Games opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 38, \"end\": 47, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.7867473906403517, \"rank\": 0.2710560109846022, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}, {\"begin\": 84, \"end\": 97, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5966886961767583e-51, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}, {\"begin\": 118, \"end\": 125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"score\": 0.9987562812085081, \"rank\": 0.0008823769274388009, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\"}, {\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.9816258228647449, \"rank\": 0.0187178876284175, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They drove around Paris in a bus emblazoned with the wordsSTOP ATTACKS ON CHRISTIANSand images of the ceremony's scenes that offended millions of Christians as well as Muslim nations.\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 384, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 219, \"end\": 224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999254214, \"rank\": 7.450881533916725e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 347, \"end\": 357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.9816258228647449, \"rank\": 0.0187178876284175, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}, {\"begin\": 369, \"end\": 375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.800513816965529, \"rank\": 0.24919767586046243, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bus was driven around the city for 10-hours without incident from 9am on Monday (August 5) before law enforcement officers surrounded it and stopped it at gunpoint and arrested those on board.\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The protesters were reportedly handcuffed, strip-searched, denied access to their devices, and held in police custody overnight without food or water on \\\"non-existent charges\\\".\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 759, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Christian campaigner Carole Farrow toldPremier Christian Newsthey were subjected to \\\"severe psychological pressure\\\" and illegally denied contact with lawyers and family members.\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 808, \"end\": 817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.7867473906403517, \"rank\": 0.2710560109846022, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She claimed the police were under orders from \\\"high-level political authorities\\\" despite the activists \\\"not violating any local laws\\\".\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Those arrested were members ofCitizenGO, a Madrid-based conservative advocacy group that engages in activism primarily by circulating online petitions.\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1226, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of them posted on social media: \\\"They escorted our bus out of Paris shortly after unjustly arresting us.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1293, \"end\": 1298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999254214, \"rank\": 7.450881533916725e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are tyrannical, anti-Christian bullies.\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1357, \"end\": 1371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Persecution_of_Christians\", \"score\": 0.9996936339450349, \"rank\": 0.00030165901770013446, \"text\": \"anti-Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Persecution_of_Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Persecution_of_Christians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's absurd.\\\"\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1394, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The protestors were released after twelve hours in police custody.\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris public prosecutor's office said it had lifted the custody order and closed the case \\\"due to an irregularity as the time limit for presentation to a judicial police officer was too late and the reason for the arrests was not sufficiently precise.\\\"\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1467, \"end\": 1472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999254214, \"rank\": 7.450881533916725e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CitizenGOquoted a French lawyer who said: \\\"It appears impossible to constitute the crime of failing to communicate a protest because there is no protest in the presence of one unique vehicle.\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1739, \"end\": 1745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9354374650292645, \"rank\": 0.06786234480473875, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The prosecutor pushed the law to its limits to stop the bus and limit their free speech.\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 2001, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Moreover, the procedure was irregular.\\\"\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The bus protest was linked to aCitizenGOpetition demanding an apology from theInternational Olympic Committeefor its opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It read in part: \\\"We have just been humiliated on the world stage!\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2244, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our Christian faith was openly mocked in the most offensive way imaginable.\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2320, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2249, \"end\": 2258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.7867473906403517, \"rank\": 0.2710560109846022, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This grotesque spectacle was an affront to everything we hold sacred, and it cannot go unchallenged.\\\"\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2422, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This was a deliberate and vicious parody humiliating our most cherished beliefs as Christians.\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2508, \"end\": 2518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.9816258228647449, \"rank\": 0.0187178876284175, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They know we are an easy target.\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And until we stop them, they will keep doing it.\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is about standing up for our faith and ensuring that such blatant profanity is never repeated.\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What happens if we stay silent?\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our faith, our Christian symbols, will become a permanent parody promoted by LGBT lobbies, backed by our globalist leaders and the international left,\\\" the petition continued.\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2749, \"end\": 2758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.7867473906403517, \"rank\": 0.2710560109846022, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}, {\"begin\": 2811, \"end\": 2815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\", \"score\": 0.999602578700409, \"rank\": 0.0003635675951101923, \"text\": \"LGBT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It had received nearly 400,000 signatures as of Thursday (August 8).\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2978, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CitizenGOfounder Ignacio Arsuaga alleged, without evidence, that police were dispatched to stop the bus by a French prosecutor under the orders of French President